x^{2} + 1 - [(x + h)^{2} + 1]
(x-(x+h))(x+x+h)
a^2-b^2=(a-b)(a+b).
x^2-1-[(x+h)^2+1]=x^2-(x+h)^2,
(x-(x+h))(x+(x+h))=-h(2x+h),
x^2+1-[(x+h)^2+1]=x^2-(x+h)^2=(x-(x+h))(x+(x+h))
\begin{align*}(x-(x+h))(x+x+h) & = (x-(x+h))(x+(x+h)) \\ & = x^2 -(x+h)^2 \\ & =  x^2 + 1 -(x+h)^2 - 1\\ & = (x^2 + 1) -[(x+h)^2 + 1] \end{align*} 
